    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic and reliable vehicle! It's in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth ride and a clean interior that makes every commute enjoyable. While you'll find some typical signs of use from its time on the road, it remains a sturdy and dependable choice for anyone looking for quality and value. Come see why this well-maintained car is the perfect fit for your next journey!",
