    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and would best suit someone looking for a project car or a budget-friendly fixer-upper. The exterior shows significant wear, including several noticeable dents, clear coat peeling on the roof, and some areas of surface rust. Inside, the upholstery has multiple tears and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, it currently runs but will require immediate attention to the suspension and likely a transmission service in the near future. It\u2019s a rough diamond that needs a lot of work to return to its former glory.",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, representing the pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like luster with zero scratches, dings, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, with the leather still smelling fresh and showing no signs of wear or creasing. Mechanically, it has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, ensuring it drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own an impeccably preserved vehicle that needs nothing.",
      "price": 49000.0,
